body:
Hey @waketzheng ,  Can you test this once.
- you'll have to install from source following directions here: [installing-from-source](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/tree/master/tools/distrib/python/grpcio_tools#installing-from-source)
- Verify that  generated code in [helloworld-example](https://sourcegraph.com/github.com/grpc/grpc/-/blob/examples/python/helloworld/helloworld_pb2_grpc.py#:~:text=%2B%20f%27%20but%20the%20generated%20code%20in%20helloworld_pb2_grpc.py%20depends%20on%27) is correct with your suggested changes.
